entry.title: How Putin's Right-Hand Man Took Out Prigozhin
entry.content: Nikolai Patrushev, a top ally of the Russian leader for decades, put in motion the assassination of the mutinous chief of the Wagner mercenary group.

entry.title: How Three Babies Were Left Behind at an Evacuated Gaza Hospital
entry.content: Palestinian medical workers and Israeli officials described a chaotic chain of events leading up to the evacuation at Al-Nasr Hospital last month, with both sides at odds over who was to blame.
